Tottenham to Play Hearts in Europa League; Rangers Meet Maribor

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-08-05T12:18:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-05/tottenham-to-play-hearts-in-europa-league-rangers-meet-maribor.html
Tottenham will meet Heart of
Midlothian in the playoff round of soccer’s Europa League, as
Rangers take on Maribor of Slovenia  The matchups were among 38 determined today by a draw in
Nyon,  Switzerland . Fulham will play Dnipro of Ukraine and
Birmingham meets Nacional of  Portugal . Celtic and Stoke face
Swiss opposition in Sion and Thun, respectively  The two-match series will be played Aug. 18 and 25 with the
winners moving into the group stage of  Europe ’s second-tier club
competition. The teams listed first will play their opening
matches at home.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  